-d { POSTDATA }  https://{URL}/v1/projects/BRAND_NEW/topics/monitoring:modifyAcl?key=S3CR3T   Responses  Success Response 200 OK  Errors  If the to-be updated ACL contains users that are non-existent in the project the API returns the following error: 404 NOT_FOUND  {
